## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="c2c3a-321">次の例では、作成、<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.Prompt>文字列からオブジェクトへの引数として、オブジェクトを渡すと、<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.Speak%2A>メソッド。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c2c3a-321">The following example creates a <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.Prompt> object from a string and passes the object as an argument to the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.Speak%2A> method.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
using System;  
using System.Speech.Synthesis;  
  
namespace SampleSynthesis  
{  
  class Program  
  {  
